@emcorinne Hello Emily,
we apologise for the delay on our reply. If we can still be of assistance, please let us know, confirming us your ticket number and your KTN by DM.
Thank you.

@mcjacintolx Olá Maria,
apresentamos as nossas sinceras desculpas pela situação e pelo inconveniente causado. Se pudermos ajudar com alguma questão, de alguma forma, por esta via, estamos ao dispor.
Obrigado.

@milophal1 ilkeraslan,
we verify that your booking is already cancelled and that you have requested the refund only of your return flight. Do you want the refund of the entire booking or do you want to rebook your flight from Manchester to Lisbon?
Thank you.

